\c 17
\s Tsvimbo yaAroni
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 2 Taura kuvana vaIsraeri, ugotora kubva kune umwe neumwe wavo tsvimbo zvichienderana neimba yemadzibaba, pamachinda avo ese zvichienderana neimba yemadzibaba avo, tsvimbo gumi nembiri. Nyora zita reumwe neumwe patsvimbo yake.
\v 3 Zvino uchanyora zita raAroni patsvimbo yaRevhi; nokuti tsvimbo imwe \add ichava\add* yemusoro weimba yemadzibaba avo.
\v 4 Zvino uchadziisa mutende rekusangana pamberi pechipupuriro, pandinosangana nemwi\x + Eki. 25.22.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino zvichati tsvimbo yemurume wandichasarudza ichabuka\x + 16.5.\x*, uye ndichagumisa kubva pandiri kugunun'una kwevana vaIsraeri kwavanokugunun'unirai nako\x + 16.11.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Mozisi wakataura kuvana vaIsraeri; nemachinda ese avo akamupa tsvimbo, imwe tsvimbo kune umwe neumwe muchinda, zvichienderana nedzimba dzemadzibaba avo, tsvimbo gumi nembiri; netsvimbo yaAroni yaiva pakati petsvimbo dzavo.
\v 7 Mozisi ndokuisa tsvimbo pamberi paJehovha mutende rechipupuriro\x + 16.8. Eki. 38.21. Num. 18.2. 2 Makor. 24.6. Mab. 7.44.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino kwakati chifume Mozisi wakapinda mutende rechipupuriro, zvino tarira, tsvimbo yaAroni yeimba yaRevhi yakabuka, ndokubudisa mabukira, ndokubudisa maruva, ndokubereka maarimondi*.
\v 9 Zvino Mozisi wakabudisira tsvimbo dzose kubva pamberi paJehovha kuvana vaIsraeri vese; zvino vakatarira vakatora umwe neumwe tsvimbo yake.
\p
\v 10 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Dzosera tsvimbo yaAroni pamberi pechipupuriro\x + 3.7; 18.3,4,5; 19.9.\x*, ichengeterwe\x + VaHeb. 9.4.\x* chiratidzo kune vakandipandukira\x + 16.38.\x*; kuti upedze kugunun'una kwavo kwandiri, kuti vasafa\x + 17.5.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino Mozisi wakaita Jehovha sezvaakamuraira, ndizvo zvaakaita.
\v 12 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakataura kuna Mozisi vachiti: Tarira, tofa, topera, topera tese.
\v 13 Umwe neumwe anoswedera, anoswedera kutabhenakeri yaJehovha achafa; tichapera kufa kanhi\x + 1.51; 3.10,38; 18.4,7,22.\x*?